
** Remove Tablespace

  - Clean all the TS data.
  - Take the TS offline.
  - Drop the TS.

** Remove a OS File from The Tablespace

  - It's not possible. The only solution would be to move the data to
    another TS and then drop the TS entirely.

  - See also 'alter table move ...'

** OMF

  <example>
    -- autoextent is on
    SQL> create tablespace ts;
    SQL> create tablespace ts datafile maxsize 800m;
    -- 2 datafiles
    -- autoextent is off because of the size specifiaction.
    SQL> create tablespace ts datafile size 200m, size 200m;
  </example>
